
HashMap Mistake Notes (Important)
1️⃣ Always be clear: What is key? What is value?
Decide first:
value → index ✅ (correct for major problems)
NOT index → value ❌
👉 Ask yourself:
“What do I need to find quickly?”

2️⃣Pattern to remember (template)
if (map.containsKey(nums[i])) {
    check condition using previous index
}
update map with current index
}
